title: Sublime Text 3 (3083) Windows

Sublime Text 3 (3083) Windows
=============================

This torrent only consists of the patched sublime text
 3 portable build 3083 zip archives and installers for
 x32 and x64 (the installers are not patched).

It contains the following files:

* ST3b3083.zip
* ST3b3083i.exe
* ST3b3083x64.zip
* ST3b3083x64i.exe
* sublime_text_patched.exe
* sublime_text_patched_x64.exe
* sublime_text_unpatched.exe
* sublime_text_unpatched_x64.exe
* info.txt
* Sublime-Text-3-3083-Windows--md5-list.chks

This is how you install sublime text 3:

- Run 'ST3b3083x64i.exe' (x64) or 'ST3b3083i.exe' (x32)
- Copy 'sublime_text_patched_x64.exe' (x64) or 'sublime_text_patched.exe' (x32) as 'sublime_text.exe' to the installation directory

This is how you install sublime text 3 portable:

- Extract 'ST3b3083x64.zip' (x64) or 'ST3b3083.zip' (x32)

You can check the files using md5sum like this:

$ md5sum -c ./Sublime-Text-3-3083-Windows--md5-list.chks
